<item>
            <title>[HBASE-2804] [replication] Support ICVs in a master-master setup</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-2804</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently an ICV ends up as a Put in the HLogs, which ReplicationSource ships to ReplicationSink that in turn only recreates the Put and not the ICV itself. This means that in a master-master replication setup where the same counters are implemented on both side, the Puts will actually overwrite each other.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We need to find a way to support this use case.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
